<BODY>
<DIV1 TYPE="answer">
<PB N="1" REF="000967_0011_0FAE398A36BF4A10">
<HEAD>Go&s;pel Order Revived, &amp;c.</HEAD>
<P>THe two fir&s;t Que&s;tions might have been wholy &s;pared, yet may &s;erve as a good introduction to others of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> a&s;pect.</P>
<P><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">. 1. <HI>Whether particular Churches ought to con&s;ist of Saints and true Believers in Chri&s;t?</HI></P>
<P>It is granted that the matter of a particular Church (for the Que&s;tion is not &s;tated with reference to the Catholick) is vi&s;ible Saints. And tho' the An&s;wer is not given in the words, yet we would charitably hope his &s;en&s;e is the &s;ame, with the united Mini|&s;ters in <HI>London.</HI>
